    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִלְחוֹ הֶעֱבִרַתּוּ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"119\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"97\" data-sentence-id=\"1\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-120\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-4\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\"><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2852\" data-full-name=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II\" data-name-he=\"רבן שמעון בן גמליאל\">רַבָּן שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן גַּמְלִיאֵל</span> אוֹמֵר: בִּזְמַן שֶׁהַקֶּרַע</a>",
