    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">רַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>: הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2852\" data-full-name=\"Rabban Shimon ben Gamliel II\" data-name-he=\"רבן שמעון בן גמליאל\">כְּרַבָּן שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן גַּמְלִיאֵל</span>. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">אַבָּיֵי</span>: הֲלָכָה — מִכְּלָל דִּפְלִיגִי? אֲמַר לֵיהּ: מַאי נָפְקָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָךְ מִינַּהּ? אֲמַר לֵיהּ: גְּמָרָא גְּמוֹר, זְמוֹרְתָּא תְּהֵא? <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"121\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"98\" data-sentence-id=\"3\">§</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-122\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\"><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-123\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">בָּשָׂר הַנִּכְנָס לַעֲבוֹדָה זָרָה מוּתָּר</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"122\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> מַאן</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-123\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">תַּנָּא? אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Ḥiyya bar Abba, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1091\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Ḥiyya bar Abba\" data-name-he=\"רבי חייא בר אבא\">רַבִּי חִיָּיא בַּר אַבָּא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1570\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוחנן\">רַבִּי יוֹחָנָן</span>: דְּלָא</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-123\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\"><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"467\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat\" data-name-he=\"רבי אלעזר בן פדת\">כְּרַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר</span>, דְּאִי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"467\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Pedat\" data-name-he=\"רבי אלעזר בן פדת\">כְּרַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר</span>, הָאָמַר:</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-123\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">סְתָם מַחְשֶׁבֶת גּוֹי לַעֲבוֹדָה</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-123\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">זָרָה</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"123\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-124\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">וְהַיּוֹצֵא אָסוּר, מִפְּנֵי שֶׁהוּא כְּזִבְחֵי</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-124\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/29b#gemara-line-6\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 29b\">מֵתִים</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"124\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> מַאי טַעְמָא? אִי אֶפְשָׁר דְּלֵיכָּא תִּקְרוֹבֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֲבוֹדָה זָרָה. מַנִּי? <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda ben Beteira I, second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1423\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda ben Beteira I\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה בן בתירא\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה בֶּן בְּתֵירָא</span> הִיא.",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>דְּתַנְיָא: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda ben Beteira I, second-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"1423\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda ben Beteira I\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה בן בתירא\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה בֶּן בְּתִירָא</span> אוֹמֵר: מִנַּיִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְתִקְרוֹבֶת עֲבוֹדָה זָרָה שֶׁמְּטַמֵּא בְּאֹהֶל?",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁנֶּאֱמַר: ״וַיִּצָּמְדוּ לְבַעַל פְּעוֹר וַיֹּאכְלוּ זִבְחֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵתִים״, מָה מֵת מְטַמֵּא בְּאֹהֶל, אַף תִּקְרוֹבֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עֲבוֹדָה זָרָה מְטַמְּאָה בְּאֹהֶל<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"125\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"99\" data-sentence-id=\"6\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הַהוֹלְכִין לַתַּרְפּוּת —",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲסוּרִין לָשֵׂאת וְלָתֵת עִמָּהֶם<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"126\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>: גּוֹי הַהוֹלֵךְ לַתַּרְפּוּת, בַּהֲלִיכָה —",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "אָסוּר, דְּאָזֵיל וּמוֹדֵי קַמֵּי עֲבוֹדָה זָרָה, בַּחֲזָרָה — מוּתָּר, מַאי דַהֲוָה הֲוָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>יִשְׂרָאֵל",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "הַהוֹלֵךְ לַתַּרְפּוּת — בַּהֲלִיכָה מוּתָּר, דִּלְמָא הָדַר בֵּיהּ וְלָא אָזֵיל; בַּחֲזָרָה אָסוּר, כֵּיוָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אֵין עָלָיו קוֹרֶט דָּם</b> אחר הפשטו אירע בו כך ולא לעבודת כוכבים:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מִכְּלָל דִּפְלִיגִי</b> מיבעיא קבעי לה מיניה מי פליגי רבנן עליה אי לא:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ומאי</span> נָפְקָא לָךְ מִינַּהּ</b> בין חלוקין בין לא חלוקין הלכה כמותו: <b>א\"ל</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>גְּמָרָא גְּמוֹר, זְמוֹרְתָּא תְּהֵא.</b> בתמיה. אביי תלמידו של רב יוסף וקא\"ל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אתה מלמדנו לומר הלכה כמותו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ותהא כזמר בעלמא דאי אין חולקין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:3:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הלכה למה לי: <b>בָּשָׂר הַנִּכְנָס <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לעבודת</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>כוכבים.</b> שהעובד כוכבים רוצה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להכניסו מותר בהנאה אם נזהר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ישראל ליטלו עם כניסתו קודם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שיקריבו אותו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מַאן תַּנָּא.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דבשר העובד כוכבים מותר בהנאה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ר\"א בשחיטת חולין בהשוחט (חולין דף"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לח:): <b>סְתָם מַחְשֶׁבֶת <span class=\"dh-divergent\">וכו&#x27;</span>.</b> וכי שחטה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עבדה לעבודת כוכבים בשחיטתו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונאסרה דשחיטתה היא תקרובתה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:4:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מָה מֵת מְטַמֵּא בְּאֹהֶל, <span class=\"dh-divergent\">כו&#x27;</span>.</b> ומינה מה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מת אסור בהנאה כדגמרינן בסנהדרין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "(<a href=\"/avodah_zarah/47b\">דף מז:</a>) ותמת שם מרים שם שם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מעגלה ערופה אף תקרובת עבודת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כוכבים אסורה בהנאה: <b>לַתַּרְפּוּת.</b> לבקש טעותן למקום אחר: ה\"ג אמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שמואל עובד כוכבים ההולך לתרפות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בהליכה אסור דאזיל ומודי בחזרה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מותר מאי דהוה הוה ישראל ההולך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לתרפות בהליכה מותר דלמא הדר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביה ולא אזיל בחזרה אסור כיון",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאביק בה הדר אזיל והתניא כו':",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 32b:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
